Windows hosts entries to block some email tracking services.

To use, you must edit your Windows hosts file and add the entries below.

Directions:
1. Run Notepad as an admin and open %windir%\system32\drivers\etc
2. Add/append the entries below to the file and save it. Make sure your hosts file is not set to read-only.

127.0.0.1 btag.it
127.0.0.1 bl-1.com
127.0.0.1 didtheyreadit.com
